      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to the highest possible standards of automotive excellence. This unit presents in showroom condition, featuring an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory freshness. Meticulously inspected and preserved, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled integrity. Every detail reflects a commitment to superior care, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
