    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty\u2014it's basically brand new and looks absolutely stunning inside and out. I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one for you! Seriously, it's in flawless shape. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
