      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 is a pristine example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering. The F22C1 power plant remains internally stock, delivering linear power delivery through the VTEC crossover point with zero parasitic loss. The 6-speed close-ratio manual gearbox provides crisp, short-throw engagement, paired perfectly with the factory Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. Chassis rigidity is maintained by the iconic X-bone frame, while the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension retains original geometry and damping characteristics. Meticulously maintained with no signs of thermal stress or mechanical wear, this unit represents the pinnacle of analog driver engagement.",
